It's actually funny, if you're bored, sit in the bazaar for a few hours with a beer (in real life) and count the number of times you see the following questions:<br>
<br>
1) Where do I buy the Trader Satchels?<br>
<br>
2) How do I look at people's stuff?<br>
<br>
3) Can I just click on them like a merchant and buy stuff?<br>
<br>
4) Is there ANY Wizard/Enchanter here who is NOT AFK?!?!<br>
<br>
5) I am selling item X 2cp less than the lowest price listed!<br>
<br>
6) Can I sell my horse back? Where? How much will I get back?<br>
<br>
7) Anyone selling KEI/C3/C4?<br>
<br>
Heh, lots of fun...<br>
